name: Bruisers of the Immaculate Tram
description: Receiving aid from the Mohoe in a time of great need, the Bruisers of the Immaculate Tram were left with a deep seated gratitude towards the Mohoe. They also were involved in the initial conception of the Thespin Skytram. Now serving as caretakers of Mohoan Larvae, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
